description._content: Programming for the JEC was conducted by the JCAA--Jewish Center Activities Association and Funded by the Community Chest. JCAA was a programming powerhouse, quickly developing junior and senior orchestra's boy and girl scout troops, a theater company, adult classes and a newspaper. Summer Center Days showcased classes and cultural activities at the Center, and brought in new participants.
